    "><div class="pipf-add-to-cart-section__buttons"><div class="pipf-add-to-cart-section__buttons--container"><div class="pipf-add-to-cart-section__buy-button-container "><div class="pipf-quantity-picker "><div class="pipf-quantity-stepper"><input inputmode="numeric" aria-label="Waarde voor ingevoerde aantal" type="text" min="1" max="99" aria-describedby="pip-add-to-cart-section-quantity-picker" data-skapa="quantity-stepper@11.0.13" name="pipf-quantity-stepper-input" class="pipf-typography-label-l pipf-quantity-stepper__input" style="width: 2ch;"><span id="pip-add-to-cart-section-quantity-picker" class="pipf-quantity-stepper__sr-label">Typ een getal of gebruik de pijltjestoetsen omhoog of omlaag om de hoeveelheid te wijzigen. De minimale hoeveelheid is 1.</span><button type="button" data-skapa="button@19.0.13" aria-label="Aantal verhogen" class="pipf-btn pipf-btn--small pipf-btn--icon-tertiary pipf-quantity-stepper__increase"><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-btn__inner"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" data-skapa="ssr-icon@11.5.0" aria-hidden="true" class="pipf-svg-icon pipf-btn__icon"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M11 12.9961v6h2v-6h6v-2h-6v-6h-2v6H5v2h6z"></path></svg></span></button><button disabled="" type="button" data-skapa="button@19.0.13" aria-label="Aantal verlagen" class="pipf-btn pipf-btn--small pipf-btn--icon-tertiary pipf-quantity-stepper__decrease"><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-btn__inner"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" data-skapa="ssr-icon@11.5.0" aria-hidden="true" class="pipf-svg-icon pipf-btn__icon"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M19 13H5v-2h14v2z"></path></svg></span></button><span class="pipf-quantity-stepper__border"></span><span aria-live="assertive" class="pipf-quantity-stepper__sr-label"></span></div></div><button type="button" data-skapa="button@19.0.13" aria-label="Toevoegen aan winkelmandje" class="pipf-btn pipf-btn--emphasised pipf-btn--fluid"><span class="pipf-typography-label-m pipf-btn__inner"><span class="pipf-btn__label">Toevoegen aan winkelmandje</span></span></button></div></div></div><noscript></noscript></div><div><div class="js-buy-module pip-buy-module"></div><div class="js-igift-container"></div></div><div class="pipf-services-section pipf-services-section--hidden"><div class="pipf-services-section__header">Beschikbare services</div></div><div></div></div></div><div class="pipf-page__left-bottom-container"><div class="pipf-key-facts"><div class="sr-only">Producteigenschappen</div><ul class="pipf-key-facts__list"><li class="pipf-key-facts__list-item pipf-key-facts__list-item--hoverable"><div tabindex="0" class="pipf-key-facts__container pipf-key-facts__container__home_smart"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" data-skapa="ssr-icon@11.5.0" aria-hidden="true" class="pipf-svg-icon pipf-key-facts__icon"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="m12.0002 3.7871 8 5.4819-.0045 10.7303h-6.9955v-4.9298h-2v4.9298H4V9.2688l8.0002-5.4817zM6 10.323v7.6764h3.0002v-4.9298h6v4.9298h2.9963l.0033-7.6766-5.9996-4.1111L6 10.3229z"></path></svg><span class="pipf-key-facts__type">Werkt met IKEA Home smart</span></div></li><li class="pipf-key-facts__list-item pipf-key-facts__list-item--hoverable"><div tabindex="0" class="pipf-key-facts__container pipf-key-facts__container__wireless_dimming"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" data-skapa="ssr-icon@11.5.0" aria-hidden="true" class="pipf-svg-icon pipf-key-facts__icon"><path d="M13 12h4c0-2.5-2-5.0048-5-5-2.5975.0041-4.4453 1.8753-4.8944 4h.0334C8.0386 7.9933 13 8.3626 13 12z"></path><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M9.9316 22c0-4.4183-3.5817-8-8-8v-2c5.5229 0 10 4.4772 10 10h-2z"></path><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M5.9316 22c0-2.2091-1.7908-4-4-4v-2c3.3138 0 6 2.6863 6 6h-2z"></path><path d="M3.8445 21.9509c-.5363.5363-1.4059.5363-1.9422 0-.5364-.5363-.5364-1.4059 0-1.9423.5363-.5363 1.4059-.5363 1.9422 0 .5364.5364.5364 1.406 0 1.9423zM5.2899 10C6.1504 7.1085 8.8289 5 12 5c3.866 0 7 3.134 7 7 0 3.3511-2.3548 6.1522-5.5 6.8389v2.0367C17.7566 20.1614 21 16.4595 21 12c0-4.9706-4.0294-9-9-9-4.2832 0-7.8675 2.992-8.777 7H5.29z"></path></svg><span class="pipf-key-facts__type">Draadloos dimmen</span></div></li></ul></div><div class="pipf-product-summary"><p class="pipf-product-summary__description">Laat je creativiteit de vrije loop en decoreer met licht. Je kan deze led-strip op de gewenste lengte knippen en moeiteloos besturen met de IKEA Home Smart app. Perfect voor boven kasten, bij de televisie of onder een bank.</p><div class="pipf-product-summary__product-info-container"><span data-skapa="product-identifier@9.0.9" class="pipf-product-identifier"><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-typography-regular pipf-product-identifier__label">Artikelnummer</span><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-product-identifier__value">404.973.95</span></span></div></div><div id="pip-product-information-section" class="pipf-product-information-section"><ul id="product-information-section-list" role="list" data-skapa="list-view@0.13.2" class="pipf-list-view pipf-list-view--large"><li id="pipf-product-information-section-list-0" class="pipf-list-view-item pipf-chunky-header__details"><button class="pipf-list-view-item__action"><span class="pipf-list-view-item__wrapper"><span class="pipf-list-view-item__label-container"><span class="pipf-text pipf-typography-label-m pipf-list-view-item__title"><span role="heading" aria-level="2">Productdetails</span></span></span></span><span class="pipf-list-view-item__control-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" data-skapa="ssr-icon@11.5.0" aria-hidden="true" class="pipf-svg-icon"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="m20.0008 12.0001-8-8.001-1.4143 1.414L16.1727 11H4v2h12.1723l-5.5868 5.5866 1.4141 1.4142 8.0012-8.0007z"></path></svg></span></button></li><li id="pipf-product-information-section-list-1" class="pipf-list-view-item pipf-chunky-header__technical"><button class="pipf-list-view-item__action"><span class="pipf-list-view-item__wrapper"><span class="pipf-list-view-item__label-container"><span class="pipf-text pipf-typography-label-m pipf-list-view-item__title"><span role="heading" aria-level="2">Technische informatie</span></span></span></span><span class="pipf-list-view-item__control-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" data-skapa="ssr-icon@11.5.0" aria-hidden="true" class="pipf-svg-icon"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="m20.0008 12.0001-8-8.001-1.4143 1.414L16.1727 11H4v2h12.1723l-5.5868 5.5866 1.4141 1.4142 8.0012-8.0007z"></path></svg></span></button></li><li id="pipf-product-information-section-list-2" class="pipf-list-view-item pipf-chunky-header__measurement"><button class="pipf-list-view-item__action"><span class="pipf-list-view-item__wrapper"><span class="pipf-list-view-item__label-container"><span class="pipf-text pipf-typography-label-m pipf-list-view-item__title"><span role="heading" aria-level="2">Afmetingen</span></span></span></span><span class="pipf-list-view-item__control-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" focusable="false" width="24" height="24" data-skapa="ssr-icon@11.5.0" aria-hidden="true" class="pipf-svg-icon"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="m20.0008 12.0001-8-8.001-1.4143 1.414L16.1727 11H4v2h12.1723l-5.5868 5.5866 1.4141 1.4142 8.0012-8.0007z"></path></svg></span></button></li></ul><div class="pipf-seo-content"><div class="pipf-product-details-modal"><h2 class="pipf-product-details-modal__title">Productdetails</h2><div class="pipf-product-details-modal__container"><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Het licht van deze LED-verlichtingsstrip creëert een gezellige sfeer, waar je hem ook neerzet.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">De led-verlichtingsstrip is buigbaar zodat je deze heel eenvoudig achter de tv of een boekenkast kan bevestigen.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Je kan de verlichtingsstrip heel makkelijk korter maken door deze te knippen op de plekken die zijn gemarkeerd met een klein schaarsymbool.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Gemakkelijk te bevestigen - verwijder gewoon het papier van de zelfklevende tape en plak de verlichtingsstrip waar je hem wil hebben.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Je kan de stemming in de kamer snel en gemakkelijk veranderen door de verlichting te dimmen en de kleur van de verlichting te wijzigen.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">De verlichtingsstrip wordt geleverd met een driver die je kan aansluiten op een stopcontact.</p><div><span role="none" class="pipf-product-details-modal__header">Designer</span><p role="none" class="pipf-product-details-modal__label">IKEA of Sweden</p></div></div><span data-skapa="product-identifier@9.0.9" class="pipf-product-identifier"><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-typography-regular pipf-product-identifier__label">Artikelnummer</span><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-product-identifier__value">404.973.95</span></span><div><h3 class="pipf-product-details-modal__section-title">Goed om te weten.</h3><div class="pipf-product-details-modal__container"><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Dit product maakt deel uit van ons assortiment voor een slim huis. Verbind het (samen met andere slimme producten) met de DIRIGERA hub en de IKEA Home smart app voor meer functies en mogelijkheden.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Gebruik ook de afstandsbediening om je lichtbron te bedienen.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">De led-lichtbron is geïntegreerd.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Download de app IKEA Home smart gratis via Google Play of de App Store, afhankelijk van de telefoon of tablet die je hebt.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Kan op de gewenste afmeting worden gesneden.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Dit slimme product kan niet worden verbonden met een TRÅDFRI hub.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">De afstandsbediening wordt apart verkocht.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Verbindingshub wordt apart verkocht.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Om gebruik te kunnen maken van een stemassistent, kan je verbinding maken met Amazon Alexa, de Woning-app van Apple of Google Home door integratie met de IKEA Home smart app.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">IKEA of Sweden AB SE-343 81 Älmhult, IKEA.com</p></div></div><div><h3 class="pipf-product-details-modal__section-title">Materialen en onderhoud</h3><div><h4 class="pipf-product-details-modal__material-header">Materiaal</h4><div class="pipf-product-details-modal__container"><dl class="pipf-product-details-modal__section"><dt>Omhulsel:</dt><dd>polycarbonaat</dd></dl><dl class="pipf-product-details-modal__section"><dt>Afdeklijst:</dt><dd>Urethaan (kunststof)</dd></dl><dl class="pipf-product-details-modal__section"><dt>Snoerklem:</dt><dd>versterkte polyamide</dd></dl></div><h4 class="pipf-product-details-modal__care-header">Onderhoud</h4><div class="pipf-product-details-modal__container"><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__label">Afnemen met een doekje met wat mild schoonmaakmiddel.</p><p class="pipf-product-details-modal__label">Nadrogen met een droge doek.</p></div></div></div><div><h3 class="pipf-product-details-modal__section-title">Veiligheid en naleving</h3><div class="pipf-product-details-modal__container"><span class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Alleen voor gebruik binnenshuis.</span><span class="pipf-product-details-modal__paragraph">Dit product is voorzien van de CE-markering</span></div></div><div><h3 class="pipf-product-details-modal__section-title">Montage en documenten</h3><div class="pi