ation-modal__product-description">Led-strip, smart draadloos dimbaar/gekleurd en wit spectrum, 4 m</p><span data-skapa="product-identifier@9.0.9" class="pipf-product-identifier"><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-typography-regular pipf-product-identifier__label">Artikelnummer</span><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-product-identifier__value">404.973.95</span></span><div class="pipf-table pipf-technical-information-modal__table"><table data-skapa="table@5.1.5"><tbody class="pipf-technical-information-modal__table"><tr><td>Handelsmerk</td><td>IKEA</td></tr><tr><td>Modelnummer</td><td>L2112</td></tr><tr><td>Energie-efficiëncyklasse</td><td>E</td></tr><tr><td>Energieverbruik van de lichtbron in de ingeschakelde modus</td><td>5 kWu/1000u</td></tr><tr><td>Stroomverbruik in standbystand</td><td>0,3 Watt</td></tr><tr><td>Nominaal vermogen</td><td>5 W</td></tr><tr><td>Nominale waarde voor bruikbare lichtstroom</td><td>640 lumen</td></tr><tr><td>Kleurtemperatuur</td><td>2700 Kelvin</td></tr><tr><td>Kleurweergave</td><td>90</td></tr><tr><td>Nominale levensduur lamp</td><td>25000 h</td></tr><tr><td>Ontstekingstijd</td><td>0,5 seconden</td></tr><tr><td>Draadloos dimbaar</td><td>Ja</td></tr><tr><td>Transformator inbegrepen</td><td>Ja</td></tr><tr><td>Modelidentificatie transformator</td><td>ICPSW24-7-3</td></tr><tr><td>Max. uitgangsvermogen transformator</td><td>7 W</td></tr><tr><td>Afmetingen transformator</td><td>66 x 44 x 25 mm</td></tr><tr><td>Transformatorgewicht</td><td>52 g</td></tr><tr><td>Type driver lichtbron(nen)</td><td>Led</td></tr><tr><td>Efficiëntie transformator bij volledige belasting</td><td>81 %</td></tr><tr><td>Driver geen energieverbruik (Pno)</td><td>0.05 W</td></tr><tr><td>Driver standby (Pnet)</td><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><td>Driver standby (Psb)</td><td>N/A</td></tr><tr><td>Transformator geschikt als dimmer voor lichtbronnen</td><td>Nee</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><div class="pipf-measurements-modal"><h2 class="pipf-measurements-modal__title">Afmetingen</h2><ul class="pipf-measurements-modal__measurements-container"><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-name">Hoogte:&nbsp;</span>3 mm</li><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-name">Lengte:&nbsp;</span>4 m</li><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-name">Lichtstroom:&nbsp;</span>640 lumen</li><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-name">Vermogen:&nbsp;</span>5 W</li><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__product-measurement-name">Breedte:&nbsp;</span>12 mm</li></ul><div><h3 class="pipf-measurements-modal__section-title">Verpakking</h3><div><div class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-container"><h4 aria-label="ORMANÄS Led-strip" class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-header notranslate">ORMANÄS</h4><span aria-hidden="true">Led-strip</span><span data-skapa="product-identifier@9.0.9" class="pipf-product-identifier"><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-typography-regular pipf-product-identifier__label">Artikelnummer</span><span class="pipf-typography-label-s pipf-product-identifier__value">404.973.95</span></span><div><ul class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-container"><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-name">Breedte:&nbsp;</span>16 cm</li><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-name">Hoogte:&nbsp;</span>5 cm</li><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-name">Lengte:&nbsp;</span>16 cm</li><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-name">Gewicht:&nbsp;</span>0.45 kg</li><li class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-wrapper"><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-name">Pakket(ten):&nbsp;</span><span class="pipf-measurements-modal__package-measurement-value">1</span></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class="pipf-seo-reviews"><h2 class="pipf-seo-reviews__title">Beoordelingen</h2><div class="pipf-seo-reviews__reviews"><div class="pipf-seo-reviews__review"><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-title">Werkt perfect en mooi, maar niet goedkoop</span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-name">Wout</span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-text">Alles doet wat hij moet doen, gaat goed mee met andere lichten, instellingen zijn top. Maar het is vergeleken met veel andere LED strips best prijzig. </span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-ratingValue">4</span></div><div class="pipf-seo-reviews__review"><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-title">zeer goed</span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-name">Jp</span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-text">perfecte kleur en eenvoudig te plaatsen</span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-ratingValue">5</span></div><div class="pipf-seo-reviews__review"><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-title">Aanrader</span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-name">Arlette</span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-text">ik vind het mooi en dat is het voornaamste!!!</span><span class="pipf-seo-reviews__review-ratingValue">4</span></div></div></div></div></div><div><div class="pipf-highlight-reviews "><div class="pipf-highlight-reviews__left-container pipf-highlight-reviews__left-container--no-highlight"><div class="pipf-highlight-reviews__header-section pipf-highlight-reviews__header-section--no-highlight"><h2 class="pipf-highlight-reviews__heading pipf-highlight-reviews__heading--no-highligh